          <salute>Dear Friend</salute>
        </opener>
        <p>
          I want you to<lb/> send me your book about<lb/> the U.G.R.R. I suppose<lb/> I could buy it although I<lb/> see it is published by subscription only.
        </p>
        <p>
	      But I want you<lb/> to send me an authorâ€™s<lb/> copy and write in it<lb/> that it is to a friend<lb/> who will never forget<lb/> the old days of the<lb/> Anti Slavery Office.
        </p>
        <closer>
          <salute>Yours truly</salute>
          <signed><persName ref="#thompsonlet">Lewis Thompson</persName><lb/>Captain 2 Calvary</signed>
